  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\ncurrent:\r\n\r\nscenario 1: resized window\r\n\r\nif we resize the window the dropdown overflows the window and is also not aligned with the original account field\r\n\r\n![Screen Shot 2022-08-04 at 10 08 59 AM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/176720/182868111-2351839c-e731-45bd-aa91-562ad5fadd1d.png)\r\n\r\nscenario 2: If the dropdown has a lot of items, it will overflow the current window\r\n\r\n<img width=\"688\" alt=\"172961203-41d33525-8564-4d6c-819d-784fe1712117\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/176720/182868345-b425636f-614c-4aba-b20d-13a7a9d7aa08.png\">\r\n\r\nexpected:\r\n\r\n- [ ] The dropdown should always keep a minimum distance from the bottom of the window\r\n- [ ] If there too many items that exceed the maximum allowed height, then the dropdown should have a scroll\r\n\r\n<img width=\"743\" alt=\"172961241-dcc9f298-5ed9-4762-a299-842c23f848ea\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/176720/182868713-c9ed318f-86e1-424e-b3dc-6bf52eaec4bc.png\">\r\n",
